                        quat. <a class="more-link" href="page.html">Read more</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <!-- end .box -->
                <div class="box box_small box2">
                    <img src="@Url.Content("~/Content/images/medium-tabs.png")" alt="" />
                    <h3>
                        Tabs and Docking</h3>
                    <p>
                        Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum <strong>dolore
                            eu fugiat</strong> nulla pariatur.<br />
